\ Model Cutting Stock Problem with Waste Minimization and Maximum Utilization
\ LP format - for model browsing. Use MPS format to capture full model detail.
Minimize
  + 10000 Constant
Subject To
 R0: <= 10000
 R1: x[0] >= 1
 R2: x[1] >= 1
 R3: x[2] >= 1
 R4: x[3] >= 1
 R5: x[4] >= 1
 R6: x[5] >= 1
 R7: x[6] >= 1
 R8: x[7] >= 1
 R9: x[8] >= 1
 R10: x[9] >= 1
 R11: x[10] >= 1
 R12: <= 1e+06
Bounds
 Constant = 1
End
